      "content": "It's heartbreaking to hear that the sting of failure and shame is so severe it's threatening your mental health and self-worth. Feeling like you're a public embarrassment and that you're dragging others down is a heavy burden to carry. Consider reaching out to a mental health professional for support, as they can help you navigate these feelings and develop coping strategies. Your worth and identity extend far beyond your current struggles - don't lose sight of that.",
      "source": "target",
