      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i'm supposed to \"reach out\" but what is there even to say? \"hey, i ruined everything and now i'm a burden\"? they just look at me with pity. the pity is worse than the anger. it feels like the only way to truly respect them and myself again is to just stop being a problem for them. to just end the cycle so they don't have to deal with my failure anymore. it feels like the only logical exit.",
